import React from 'react'
import { HeaderLink } from "../header-link/header-link"
import styles from "./app-header.module.css"

function AppHeader() {
  return (
    <header className={styles.header}>
        <HeaderLink />
        <HeaderLink />
        <LogoLink />
        <HeaderLink />
    </header>
  )
}

export default AppHeader
